            value="engine.decide(symbol, prices)  [engine/trading_engine.py]&#xa;1. Compute latest indicator values (one scalar each, latest bar only):&#xa;   • SMARatioPredictor.compute(prices)[-1]&#xa;   • BollingerPercentBPredictor.compute(prices)[-1]&#xa;   • MACDHistogramPredictor.compute(prices)[-1]&#xa;2. Get current holding from tracker.holdings[symbol]&#xa;   → Map: 0 shares=FLAT(0), &gt;0=LONG(1), &lt;0=SHORT(2)&#xa;3. encoder.encode({sma_ratio, bb_pct_b, macd_hist}, holding_idx) → state int [0,1535]&#xa;   (Uses stored bin_edges from training — scale-invariant, applies to hourly data)&#xa;4. learner.best_action(state)  [model/q_learner.py]&#xa;   → argmax Q[state] — NO randomness (rar=0), NO Q-table update (pure inference)&#xa;5. Map action int → (action_str, shares):&#xa;   0=HOLD(0 shares), 1=BUY(TRADE_UNIT shares), 2=SELL(all held shares)&#xa;Return: (action_str, shares)"
            style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;
